Sofapaka on Saturday completed an epic comeback to remain in the Kenyan Premier League after their 5-1 rout of Thika United at the Kenyatta Stadium, Machakos. With Ushuru losing their final match of the 2016 season 3-1 to Posta Rangers at the Safaricom Stadium, Sofapaka completed a massive comeback to remain in the top tier. More to follow...  